description.narrative: UNICEF continues its commitment in strengthening data on children to influence policy formulation by improving institutional system capacity on planning, advocacy & monitoring of child-focused SDGs indicators, ensuring quality child-centered research and risk analysis.;UNICEF Malaysia also completed a landmark study on the impact of climate change and environmental degradation, providing critical evidence for advocating for children’s rights to a clean, safe, healthy, and sustainable environment in Malaysia.Families on the Edgestudy has also provided extensive technical inputs to debates related to Malaysia’s social protection response to COVID-19 throughout the first half of the year. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:03/02/2022
